"title": "8804: pride, examples of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8804",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Scripture illustrates the many different ways in which pride manifests itself.</p>\n<h2>Pride in status</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod5:2\">EXO 5:2</a> <em>Pharaoh</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs5:11\">2KI 5:11</a> <em>Naaman</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs20:13\">2KI 20:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:25\">2CH 32:25</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth5:11-Esth5:12\">EST 5:11–5:12</a> <em>Haman</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa16:6\">ISA 16:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer48:29\">JER 48:29</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa47:8\">ISA 47:8</a> <em>Babylon</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:49-Ezek16:50\">EZK 16:49–16:50</a> <em>Sodom</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek28:2\">EZK 28:2</a> <em>the king of Tyre</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek31:3\">EZK 31:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek31:10\">EZK 31:10</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:23\">DAN 5:23</a> <em>Belshazzar</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Obad1:3\">OBA 1:3</a> <em>Edom</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph2:15\">ZEP 2:15</a> <em>Nineveh</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:6-Matt23:7\">MAT 23:6–23:7</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:38-Mark12:39\">MRK 12:38–12:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:46\">LUK 20:46</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:43\">LUK 11:43</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:9\">ACT 8:9</a> <em>Simon the sorcerer</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:7\">REV 18:7</a> <em>Babylon the Great</em></p>\n<h2>Pride in strength</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:42\">1SA 17:42</a> <em>Goliath</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs14:9-2Kgs14:10\">2KI 14:9–14:10</a> <em>Amaziah, king of Judah</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs18:33-2Kgs18:35\">2KI 18:33–18:35</a> <em>the Assyrian commander</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa9:9-Isa9:10\">ISA 9:9–9:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos10:13\">HOS 10:13</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa10:13\">ISA 10:13</a> <em>the king of Assyria</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan3:15\">DAN 3:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:30\">DAN 4:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:33-Matt26:35\">MAT 26:33–26:35</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:29-Mark14:31\">MRK 14:29–14:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:33\">LUK 22:33</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:37\">JHN 13:37</a></p>\n<h2>Pride in wisdom</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa10:13\">ISA 10:13</a> <em>the king of Assyria</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:21\">ACT 17:21</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:22\">ROM 1:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:20\">1CO 1:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor3:18\">1CO 3:18</a></p>\n<h2>Proud ambition</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa14:13-Isa14:14\">ISA 14:13–14:14</a> <em>the king of Babylon</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:3-2Thess2:4\">2TH 2:3–2:4</a> <em>the antichrist</em></p>\n<h2>Spiritual pride</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs10:16\">2KI 10:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job32:1\">JOB 32:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job33:9\">JOB 33:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:5\">ISA 65:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:2\">MAT 6:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:3\">MAT 6:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:16\">MAT 6:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:5\">MAT 23:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:30\">MAT 23:30</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:40\">MRK 12:40</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:47\">LUK 20:47</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:14-Luke16:15\">LUK 16:14–16:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:9\">LUK 18:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:11-Luke18:12\">LUK 18:11–18:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John9:40-John9:41\">JHN 9:40–9:41</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:29\">LUK 10:29</a> <em>an expert in the law</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:33\">JHN 8:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John9:34\">JHN 9:34</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:17-Rom2:20\">ROM 2:17–2:20</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor4:7\">1CO 4:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor4:18\">1CO 4:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:17\">REV 3:17</a> <em>the church in Laodicea</em></p>",
